text.tspan: Various measures of health expenditure as share of GDP, United Kingdom,
Figures correspond to various sources of information regarding public expenditure on health care, as share of GDP. The series
'OWID extrapolated' was constructed using the other series (see Source tab for details).
Source: WHO GHED (2017), OECD.stat (2016), OECD (1993), Lindert (1994), Our World In Data based on Lindert (1994), OECD (1993),
